{"name": "jb-wattpad-scraper", "metadata": {"name": "jb-wattpad-scraper", "version": "0.0.40", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8"], "home_page": "https://github.com/josyelbuenos/jb-wattpad-scraper", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["bs4", "EbookLib", "fake-headers", "httpx"], "summary": "Get wattpad stories and chapters, and download them as ebook", "upload_time": 1735234633}, "documentation": ["Extraia hist\u00c3\u00b3rias do Wattpad com facilidade! Com este pacote, voc\u00c3\u00aa pode buscar hist\u00c3\u00b3rias, baix\u00c3\u00a1-las diretamente e at\u00c3\u00a9 convert\u00c3\u00aa-las para formatos de eBook como EPUB e PDF (em desenvolvimento).\r\n\r\nImportante: Este \u00c3\u00a9 um c\u00c3\u00b3digo baseado em no c\u00c3\u00b3digo oficial do Ayobamidele, pois como n\u00c3\u00a3o havia uma biblioteca hospedada, eu resolvi hospedar. \r\n- [GitHub do Projeto original](https://github.com/Ayobamidele/wattpad-scraper)\r\n\r\n## Funcionalidades Principais\r\n- Pesquisar hist\u00c3\u00b3rias no Wattpad.\r\n- Baixar hist\u00c3\u00b3rias utilizando a URL.\r\n- Converter hist\u00c3\u00b3rias para o formato EPUB.\r\n- Login para acessar conte\u00c3\u00bados exclusivos.\r\n\r\n### Links Importantes\r\n- [GitHub do Projeto](https://github.com/josyelbuenos/jb-wattpad-scraper)\r\n\r\n## Instala\u00c3\u00a7\u00c3\u00a3o\r\n\r\nPara instalar o pacote, basta usar o comando abaixo no terminal:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npip install jb-wattpad-scraper\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Como Usar\r\n\r\n### Baixar Hist\u00c3\u00b3ria por URL\r\n```python\r\nfrom wattpad_scraper import Wattpad\r\n\r\nwattpad = Wattpad()\r\nurl_historia = \"https://www.wattpad.com/story/162756571-bending-the-rules-the-rules-1\"\r\nhistoria = wattpad.get_book_by_url(url_historia)\r\n\r\nprint(historia.title)  # T\u00c3\u00adtulo da hist\u00c3\u00b3ria\r\nprint(historia.author.name, historia.author.url)  # Autor e link do perfil\r\nprint(historia.description)  # Descri\u00c3\u00a7\u00c3\u00a3o\r\nprint(historia.chapters[0].title, historia.chapters[0].content)  # Primeiro cap\u00c3\u00adtulo e conte\u00c3\u00bado\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Pesquisar Hist\u00c3\u00b3rias\r\n```python\r\nfrom wattpad_scraper import Wattpad\r\n\r\nwattpad = Wattpad()\r\nresultados = wattpad.search_books('romance hist\u00c3\u00b3rico', completed=True, mature=True, free=True, paid=False, limit=5)\r\n\r\nfor historia in resultados:\r\n    print(historia.title)  # Exibe os t\u00c3\u00adtulos encontrados\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Converter Hist\u00c3\u00b3ria para EPUB\r\n```python\r\nfrom wattpad_scraper import Wattpad\r\n\r\nwattpad = Wattpad()\r\nhistoria = wattpad.search_books('fantasia m\u00c3\u00a1gica')[0]\r\nhistoria.convert_to_epub()  # Converte e salva no diret\u00c3\u00b3rio atual\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Autentica\u00c3\u00a7\u00c3\u00a3o (Beta)\r\n```python\r\nfrom wattpad_scraper import Wattpad\r\n\r\nwattpad = Wattpad(\"seu_usuario\", \"sua_senha\")\r\nhistoria = wattpad.search_books(\"aventura \u00c3\u00a9pica\")[0]\r\nprint(historia.chapters[2].content)  # Conte\u00c3\u00bado do terceiro cap\u00c3\u00adtulo\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Usando Arquivo de Cookies\r\n1. Instale a extens\u00c3\u00a3o \"Cookie - Editor\" no navegador.\r\n2. Exporte os cookies e salve como um arquivo `.json`.\r\n3. Utilize no c\u00c3\u00b3digo conforme o exemplo abaixo:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom wattpad_scraper import Wattpad\r\n\r\nwattpad = Wattpad(cookie_file='/caminho/para/cookies.json')\r\nresultados = wattpad.search_books(\"hist\u00c3\u00b3rias exclusivas\")\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Contribua\r\nContribui\u00c3\u00a7\u00c3\u00b5es s\u00c3\u00a3o sempre bem-vindas! Sinta-se \u00c3\u00a0 vontade para abrir issues ou enviar pull requests.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDesenvolvido com \u00f0\u0178\u2019\u2013 para todos os f\u00c3\u00a3s de leitura.\r\n\r\n\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_download", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_download.url", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_download.t", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_download.TestDownloader", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_download.TestDownloader.test_convert_to_epub", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "wattpad_scraper.test", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_wattpad_downloader", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_wattpad_downloader.EXAMPLE_URL", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_wattpad_downloader.TestWattpadDownloader", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_wattpad_downloader.TestWattpadDownloader.test_book_exists", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_wattpad_downloader.TestWattpadDownloader.test_harry_in_tags", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "wattpad_scraper.test.test_wattpad_downloader.TestWattpadDownloader.test_find_correct_author", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "doc